sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant SP as SearchPage (React)
    participant QS as queryStore (Zustand)
    participant API as ApiClient (axios)
    participant SVC as SearchService (FastAPI)
    participant DB as DatabaseManager
    participant SQL as SQLite (cbp_rulings.db)
    participant DP as DetailPage (React)

    rect rgba(235,245,255,.35)
    note over User,SQL: 主流程 1 — 关键词搜索 + 列表
    User->>SP: 输入关键词 "toy" + 年份/状态筛选
    SP->>QS: 写入查询状态 (keyword/year/status)
    SP->>API: GET /api/rulings?keyword=toy&year=2023&status=active&page=1
    API->>SVC: 解析参数 -> SearchParams
    SVC->>DB: fetch_rulings(params)
    DB->>SQL: SELECT * FROM rulings WHERE subject LIKE ? OR description LIKE ? ... LIMIT/OFFSET
    SQL-->>DB: 匹配行 + COUNT(*) 总数
    DB-->>SVC: (rows, total)
    SVC-->>API: 200 {code:0, data: PageResult}
    API-->>SP: RulingListItem[] + 分页元数据
    SP->>SP: 渲染 ResultList / Pagination
    end

    rect rgba(240,255,240,.35)
    note over User,DP: 主流程 2 — 点击进入详情
    User->>SP: 点击卡片 (ruling_no = N12345)
    SP->>DP: 路由跳转 /ruling/N12345
    DP->>API: GET /api/rulings/N12345
    API->>SVC: 详情请求
    SVC->>DB: fetch_ruling_by_no("N12345")
    DB->>SQL: SELECT * FROM rulings WHERE ruling_no = ?
    SQL-->>DB: 1 行 (含 description / detail_url / parse_failed)
    DB-->>SVC: dict
    SVC-->>API: {code:0, data: RulingDetail}
    API-->>DP: 渲染全文 + 官方链接 + 解析失败提示
    end

    rect rgba(255,248,235,.45)
    note over User,SQL: 辅助流程 — 统计概览
    User->>SP: 点击「统计概览」入口
    SP->>API: GET /api/stats/overview
    API->>SVC: 统计请求
    SVC->>DB: fetch_stats()
    DB->>SQL: COUNT 总量 / 按年 GROUP BY / 按状态 GROUP BY / parse_failed=1
    SQL-->>DB: 统计结果
    DB-->>SVC: dict
    SVC-->>API: {code:0, data: StatsOverview}
    API-->>SP: 渲染图表
    end
